### _sp_sv_timelimit_mod

_sp_sv_timelimit_mod

Modify the timelimit counting

Values:

- 0: No (default). Counting starts from the player that has been in the server the longest.
- 1: Yes. Counting starts when the map loads.
- 2: Yes. Counting starts when the map loads. Counting stops when the game is paused and it's resumed when the game is unpaused.
